# Internal Library CLI

## Installation

```bash
# Interactive mode
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli

# Install specific component
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add <component>

# Install component with variant
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add <component> <variant>

# List all available components
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli list

# List variants for a specific component
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli list <component>
```

---

## Available Components

| Component | Variants | Dependencies | Usage Rule |
|---|---|---|---|
| `carousel` | — | embla-carousel-react, embla-carousel, cva | `custom-carousel` skill |
| `ticker` | `hover`, `non-hover` | motion | `custom-ticker` skill |
| `scroll-components` | `scroll-tracker`, `parallax-image`, `scale-gallery` | motion | `custom-scroll-tracker` skill |
| `in-view` | `grid`, `individual` | motion | `custom-inview-*` skills |
| `faqs-accordion` | — | @radix-ui/react-accordion | — |
| `lenis` | — | lenis | — |
| `strapi-dynamic-zone` | — | — | — |

