## Quick Install Examples

```bash
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add carousel
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add faqs-accordion
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add lenis
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add strapi-dynamic-zone
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add ticker hover
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add ticker non-hover
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add scroll-components scroll-tracker
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add scroll-components parallax-image
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add scroll-components scale-gallery
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add in-view grid
pnpx @androbinco/library-cli add in-view individual
```

---

## Notes

- Check if the component already exists (e.g. `src/components/carousel`) before running the install command
- Commands complete without interactive prompts — suitable for automation
- Missing dependencies are installed automatically
- Returns non-zero exit code on failure
